Usage:
  status <seed> [flags]

Examples:
# Start a seed execution with the properties and scan-type flags
	discovery ingestion seed start --scan-type FULL --properties '{"stagingBucket":"my-bucket"}' 0ce1bece-5a01-4d4a-bf92-5ca3cd5327f3

Flags:
      --details            gets more information when getting a seed execution, like the audited changes and record and job summaries
      --execution string   the id of the seed execution that will be retrieved
  -h, --help               help for status

